[I] Library for rich text and formatting in the terminal

[T] Rich is a Python library for rich text and beautiful formatting in the
[T] terminal. The Rich API makes it easy to add color and style to terminal
[T] output. Rich can also render pretty tables, progress bars, markdown, syntax
[T] highlighted source code, tracebacks, and more - out of the box.

[U] https://rich.readthedocs.io/en/latest/

